'''Keith Szarabajka''' (born [[December 2]], [[1960s#1962|1962]]) is an American actor and voice actor who voiced the [[Dewback/Legends|Dewback]] [[Desert stormtrooper/Legends|Trooper]], the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Infiltrator/Legends|Infiltrator]], and the [[TIE pilot|TIE Fighter Pilot]] in ''[[Star Wars: Force Commander]]''. He also voiced [[Cikatro Vizago]] in ''[[Star Wars Rebels]]''.

